title: Transfer your driving instructor registration to Great Britain

heading_context: Transfer your driving instructor registration to Great Britain
chunks.html_content:
Apply to transfer your Northern Ireland or European Union (EU) driving instructor registration to Great Britain. It costs £300.

This service is available from 6am to 11:30pm.

Get a criminal record disclosure number if you’ve lived in Great Britain for at least 12 months. You cannot use one you have already - you must get a new one.
chunks.plain_content:
Transfer your driving instructor registration to Great Britain
Apply to transfer your Northern Ireland or European Union (EU) driving instructor registration to Great Britain. It costs £300.
This service is available from 6am to 11:30pm.
Get a criminal record disclosure number if you’ve lived in Great Britain for at least 12 months. You cannot use one you have already - you must get a new one.

heading_context: Transfer your driving instructor registration to Great Britain
chunks.html_content: If you’ve lived in Great Britain for less than 12 months, get a ‘certificate of good character’ from the country you were living in before. You need a translation in English.
chunks.plain_content:

heading_context: Transfer your driving instructor registration to Great Britain
chunks.html_content: You’ll need to send documents to the Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (DVSA) to finish your application. DVSA will contact you and tell you what to send.
chunks.plain_content:

What happens next
You’ll need to send documents to the Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (DVSA) to finish your application. DVSA will contact you and tell you what to send.
